<script>
// Meta Pixel - Omnitag for GTM-Kit Events
// Requires: Set 'Meta Pixel ID' variable to your Pixel ID
(function() {
  var pixelId = {{Meta Pixel ID}};
  if (!pixelId || typeof fbq !== 'function') return;

  var eventName = {{Event}};
  var ecommerce = {{DLV - ecommerce}} || {};

  // Event mapping: GTM-Kit/GA4 -> Meta
  var eventMap = {
    'page_view': 'PageView',
    'view_item': 'ViewContent',
    'view_item_list': 'ViewContent',
    'select_item': 'ViewContent',
    'add_to_cart': 'AddToCart',
    'view_cart': 'ViewContent',
    'begin_checkout': 'InitiateCheckout',
    'add_payment_info': 'AddPaymentInfo',
    'add_shipping_info': 'AddPaymentInfo',
    'purchase': 'Purchase'
  };

  var metaEvent = eventMap[eventName];
  if (!metaEvent) return;

  var params = {};
  if (ecommerce.value !== undefined) params.value = ecommerce.value;
  if (ecommerce.currency) params.currency = ecommerce.currency;
  if (ecommerce.items && ecommerce.items.length) {
    params.content_ids = ecommerce.items.map(function(i) { return i.item_id; });
    params.content_type = 'product';
    params.contents = ecommerce.items.map(function(i) {
      return { id: i.item_id, quantity: i.quantity || 1 };
    });
    params.num_items = ecommerce.items.length;
  }
  if (ecommerce.transaction_id) params.order_id = ecommerce.transaction_id;

  fbq('track', metaEvent, params);
})();
</script>

<script>
// TikTok Pixel - Omnitag for GTM-Kit Events
// Requires: Set 'TikTok Pixel ID' variable to your Pixel ID
(function() {
  var pixelId = {{TikTok Pixel ID}};
  if (!pixelId || typeof ttq === 'undefined') return;

  var eventName = {{Event}};
  var ecommerce = {{DLV - ecommerce}} || {};

  // Event mapping: GTM-Kit/GA4 -> TikTok
  var eventMap = {
    'page_view': 'ViewContent',
    'view_item': 'ViewContent',
    'view_item_list': 'ViewContent',
    'add_to_cart': 'AddToCart',
    'begin_checkout': 'InitiateCheckout',
    'add_payment_info': 'AddPaymentInfo',
    'purchase': 'CompletePayment'
  };

  var ttEvent = eventMap[eventName];
  if (!ttEvent) return;

  var params = {};
  if (ecommerce.value !== undefined) params.value = ecommerce.value;
  if (ecommerce.currency) params.currency = ecommerce.currency;
  if (ecommerce.items && ecommerce.items.length) {
    params.contents = ecommerce.items.map(function(i) {
      return {
        content_id: i.item_id,
        content_name: i.item_name,
        quantity: i.quantity || 1,
        price: i.price
      };
    });
  }

  ttq.track(ttEvent, params);
})();
</script>
